{"type": "article", "id": 3012, "title": "PUMA全新「Clean」系列", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-23T07:28:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232938qo0QCLZ1XwbKxD9P.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t继早前发布的「Ostrich」系列之后，运动品牌 PUMA 日前又为 Court Star 带来全新的「Clean」系列,该系列包含卡其色与黑色两个版本，设计上延续了 Court Star 一直以来简约复古的鞋身设计，材质选择高质量的皮革制作而成，搭配以后跟的金色 PUMA 标志与拼接元素，及其运动鞋底。该系列将于 10 月 24 日起登陆 <a href=\"http://www.hanon-shop.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Hanon</a> 等指定零售商的网上店铺。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232936cfOIaEzijkGA6LoN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232937JVjloOmS2C9qfvdG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232937YjlUBHvtGZPqF02c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}